"{\"uid\": \"nbcchicago.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-caeleb-dressel-left-in-tears-after-missing-chance-to-defend-gold-in-50-meter-free-100-fly-3510444\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Dr. Jud Ready, a Principal Research Engineer at Georgia Tech, explains that the organizers of the Paris Olympics picked maximizing the number of seats in the swim stadium over maximizing the speed of the competition pool.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IF_Ready\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6038318058932784e-15, \"text\": \"Ready\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IF_Ready\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IF_Ready\"}, {\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Tech_Yellow_Jackets_football\", \"score\": 0.953419456867442, \"rank\": 0.04539480095890753, \"text\": \"Georgia Tech\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Tech_Yellow_Jackets_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Tech_Yellow_Jackets_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Decorated AmericanswimmerCaeleb Dressel broke down in tears on Friday atthe Summer Games in Parisas he missed chances to defend two of his Olympic titles from three years ago in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9785168372553299, \"rank\": 0.021954817201296793, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after a sixth-place showing in the 50-meter freestyle, he failed to reach the final in the 100 butterfly.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream NBC 5 for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously it's not my best work,\\\" Dressel said.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had a lot of fun though, I can honestly say that.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has not been my best week, I do not think I need to shy away from that, but the racing's been really fun here.\\\"\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bouncing along moments before his freestyle race, Dressel made his way onto the pool deck when his name was introduced looking confident as ever.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He raised his arms and side-shuffled to reach his spot in Lane 2.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel set Olympic records while winning both the 50 free and 100 fly - the latter also a world record - among his five golds at the Tokyo Games, but touched the wall in 21.61 for sixth in the free Thursday.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His fly semifinal was a shocking 13th-fastest.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old Dressel has been cheered on by wife Meghan and their five-month-old son, August, sporting oversized protective headphones in the deafening noise of La Defense Arena.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch all the action from the Paris Olympic and Paralympic Games live on Peacock  The baby did get to witness Dad bring home one gold medal.Dressel anchored the winning 4x100-meter freestyle foursome as the Americans beat out the rival Australians and Chinese on Saturday night in Day 1 of Olympic swimming competition.\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999528695309, \"rank\": 4.7130499841419365e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\", \"score\": 0.6548847941734516, \"rank\": 0.5267090581020426, \"text\": \"Dad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\"}, {\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.653450694343134, \"rank\": 0.5080391002128192, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That marked his eighth career gold.\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, he also won the 100 free and 4x100 medley relay after capturing golds in the two relays at the 2016 Rio de Janeiro Games, too.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1803, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9785168372553299, \"rank\": 0.021954817201296793, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1942, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999994654650955, \"rank\": 4.4578335361801477e-07, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}]}"